Episodes.Title: Pilot
Episodes.Plot: Longtime ER nurse Jackie Peyton bends the rules to bring some good from a patient's senseless death, while concealing her addiction to a pain killer she gets from her boyfriend, the hospital pharmacist.
Episodes.ParentalRatingReason: R16 Drug use,sex scenes and offensive language
Episodes.Writer: Liz Brixius, Linda Wallem & Evan Dunsky
